{"tid":1480522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外匯基金最 update 資產負債表 (2019年5月底)","createTime":"2019-08-17T10:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:26:27.000Z","uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb172e8e9f608cf8ca742d7d067df6e096fb1cfd","tid":1480522,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"之前一直誤會左 以為外匯儲備係全部都係現金<br />\n其實唔係 外匯儲備係講緊 外匯資產 包括股票債券<br />\n而且外匯儲備係有負債既<br />\n而外匯儲備既淨資產係少於 900 億美元<br />\n條 link 仲有更詳細既數字<br />\n大家可以慢慢研究<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhSTqo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhSTqo3.png&h=fb3367d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/chi/doc/key-information/press-release/2019/20190628c4a1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fmedia%2Fchi%2Fdoc%2Fkey-information%2Fpress-release%2F2019%2F20190628c4a1.pdf&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=d8ba390f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/chi/doc/key-information/press-release/2019/20190628c4a1.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"30417560b82401d4c5e998b05f81d8357768063d","tid":1480522,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"MK@17Aug 1857 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=caf5333f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mkwdqud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkwdqud.png&h=709b152d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"5be6dab98febfc9884ae3a530525b4c02d3a8764","tid":1480522,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep